    "output": "以下是几种常见的Python实现斐波那契数列计算的函数：\n\n### 1. 递归实现（直观但效率较低，不适合计算大n）\n```python\ndef fibonacci_recursive(n):\n    if n <= 0:\n        return \"输入必须是正整数\"\n    elif n == 1 or n == 2:\n        return 1\n    else:\n        return fibonacci_recursive(n - 1) + fibonacci_recursive(n - 2)\n```\n\n### 2. 迭代实现（效率高，推荐使用）\n```python\ndef fibonacci_iterative(n):\n    if n <= 0:\n        return \"输入必须是正整数\"\n    elif n == 1 or n == 2:\n        return 1\n    a, b = 1, 1\n    for _ in range(3, n + 1):\n        a, b = b, a + b\n    return b\n\n# 获",
